{"tid":1223170,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"請保持清醒 抵抗三五毛 目標係撤惡法","createTime":"2019-06-14T15:40:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-14T15:45:30.000Z","uid":19992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"4e4b9b0e7de39e1b17509f45d52381b924d97d99","tid":1223170,"uid":19992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T15:40:50.000Z","msg":"我哋嘅目標係<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>撤回惡法 釋放義士</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n首先好文選讀 多謝兩位巴打<br />\n<br />\n【經驗總結】 尋日出過幾輪文宣，小弟有啲嘢想同連登嘅鍵盤戰士講<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1212748\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1212748</a><br />\n<br />\n[警告] 連登正被大量網軍攻略 請保持清醒 小心以下言論<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1222396\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1222396</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>一日未正式撤回<br />\n一日都唔可以鬆懈</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n未證實消息<br />\n麻煩大家fact check咗先 或者表明需要求證<br />\n<br />\n流料<br />\n麻煩大家幫手澄清 之後由佢沉<br />\n<br />\n消息人士鳩噏 估估下 花邊新聞 政棍發言卸膊抽水<br />\n麻煩大家無視 由佢沉<br />\n<br />\n真正有意思嘅討論<br />\n麻煩大家推Post<br />\n<br />\n我都做緊 希望推動真正資訊流通同埋有效討論<br />\n<br />\n我講多次 我哋要嘅係<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>撤回逃犯條例</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n多謝大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42a527e72dca81d21a063ed0c487648f6d9ff7b2","tid":1223170,"uid":15394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T15:45:30.000Z","msg":"係，唔好再比人轉移視線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔好意思，借一借位<br />\n<br />\n（好撚重要）提防五毛大軍洗版注意 （2）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1223122\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1223122</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}